 Biological safety: two and four weeks after each vaccination, and thereafter every 12 weeks, in reference with the baseline before the first dose, by measuring the following RBC, hemoglobin, hematocrit, platelets, WBC with differential counts, ASAT, ALAT, total bilirubin, alkaline phosphatase, GT, creatinin.

